Jacobson Stores Inc said board voted three-for-two stock split , payble March 30 , record March 13 .
In action , Jacobson 's director approved increase quarterly dividend 11 ct post split basis payable April 14 , record March 30 .
The new dividend rate represents 32 pct increase 12-1/2 ct paid quarterly pre-split basis .
